The '''''Meridian''''' was a sleek, [[black]]-[[Hull/Legends|hulled]] [[Shuttle/Legends|shuttle]] used by [[New Republic Intelligence Service|New Republic Intelligence]] to ferry the bodies of [[Doctor/Legends|Doctors]] [[Kroddok Stopa]] and [[Josala Krenn]], several recovered [[Qella]] bodies and artifacts back to [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]]. She was captained by [[Wagg]].

